data.description: *BRING ALL OFFERS* BEAUTIFULLY UPDATED 2 STORY with a POOL & SPA on a GORGEOUS GREENBELT CUL-DE-SAC! Located in highly desired Highland Shores, this home showcases extensive handscraped wood floors, recent carpet, fresh paint, wrought iron spindles, decorative lighting, a cozy fireplace & tons of windows for natural light. The chef in your family will love the modern kitchen featuring granite counters, white cabinets, a 5 burner cooktop, bay window breakfast area, under cabinet lighting & pendant lights. End your day in the remodeled primary suite boasting a frameless shower, jetted tub, granite vanities, white cabinets, 2 walk-in closets & a sitting area, or entertain family & friends in the game room with French doors that provide privacy. Relax outdoors in your spacious backyard including a sparkling pool & spa, large multi-level deck & tons of mature trees. Recent roof, pool filter & booster pump. Highland Shores offers pools, playgrounds, parks, tennis courts, trails & more!
